item.dc:creator: @The_Un-Named The Un-Named
item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

Well the first line looks like it was a log of the rs chat, the second one I can’t help you.

You where probably autoing and got a random. Here’s why I think why:

02:09:40 am f our world: he might get 1 black mark out of 10, at

That looks like a chat log, like I said earlier, he’s talking about black marks and to somebody, then you get a runtime error in SRL anti-randoms handler. How do they know your autoing? Failed random?
